### Demo Redis Caching - Test nhanh

### Bước 1: Lấy JWT Token
POST http://localhost:5050/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json
ClientId: demo-cache

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

### Bước 2: Test Caching - Request đầu tiên (slow - hit downstream)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-cache-test

### Bước 3: Test Caching - Request thứ hai (fast - from Redis cache)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-cache-test

### Bước 4: Test với ID khác nhau (different cache keys)

### Request cho ID 123 - First time (slow)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-cache-test

### Request cho ID 123 - Second time (fast - cached)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-cache-test

### Request cho ID 456 - First time (slow - different cache key)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/456
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-cache-test

### Request cho ID 456 - Second time (fast - cached)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/456
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: demo-cache-test